      • buildScript

        public List<List<String>> buildScript(List<File> files)
                               throws Exception
        Build bash script lines to classify unpaired reads with RDP. The inner list contains the bash script lines required to classify 1 sample (call java to run RDP jar on sample).

        Example line: "java -jar $RDP_PATH t /database/silva128/rRNAClassifier.properties -o ./output/sample42.fasta_reported.tsv ./input/sample42.fasta"

        Specified by:
        buildScript in interface ScriptModule
        Specified by:
        buildScript in class ScriptModuleImpl
        Parameters:
        files - Files in the input directory that contain only forward reads
        Returns:
        Nested list of bash scripts lines
        Throws:
        Exception - if unable to generate script lines
